  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      497.89,
      555.05,
      535.27
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at a few places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Southern and Uva provinces and in Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts after 2.00 p.m.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      538.93,
      378.98,
      560.47
    ],
    "text": "Mainly dry weather will prevail over the other parts of the island.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      564.25,
      554.71,
      602.59
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa and Uva provinces and in Ampara district during the early hours of the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      606.01,
      554.47,
      643.27
    ],
    "text": "The general public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      646.54,
      555.05,
      952.2
    ],
    "text": "On the apparent northward relative motion of the sun, it is going to be directly over the latitudes of Sri Lanka during 05th to 15th of April in this year. The nearest areas of Sri Lanka over which the sun is overhead tomorrow (10th) are Nagawilluwa, Galgamuwa, Sigiriya, Palugasdamana, and Mankerni about 12:11 noon.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      3.9600000381469727,
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
